data.description: Enjoy cul-de-sac living in this 3BR/2BA BRICK home on one level.  Fully applianced eat-in kitchen along with pantry closet, 2 car attached garage, and a primary suite with full bath and double closets. The rear patio area offers a quiet retreat for those warmer days, while the living room's free standing electric fireplace adds a nice bit of warmth for the cooler evenings.  Neutral decor throughout, ready for you to move right in...Don't wait or you'll miss it!
